PrecisEnactment of an ORDER AMENDING THE SCHEDULE TO THE CUSTOMS TARIFF, 1999-2 which reduces tariffs on a number of manufacturing inputs and makes technical amendments that clarify previous reductions on certain pile fabrics used for making clothing, on certain gas cylinders for automobile seats and on certain welding wire.

Attachments
precis:
Enactment of an ORDER AMENDING THE SCHEDULE TO THE CUSTOMS TARIFF, 1999-2
which reduces tariffs on a number of manufacturing inputs and makes
technical amendments that clarify previous reductions on certain pile
fabrics used for making clothing, on certain gas cylinders for automobile
seats and on certain welding wire.
